Page Preview Radiant Extension
==============================

Plug this extension in and you can view previews of pages, even if they are in "draft" mode.

A button is available on the edit page linking to the preview.
Also you can get to the page by this url structure: `/admin/pages/preview/:id`


Based on the extension found here:
http://dev.eyebeam.org/svn/radiant-partatts/radiant/vendor/extensions/page_preview/

